    {
      "id": "52012dd9-9545-44cc-8118-5048a08b3fc8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Findings show that including grade of the first semester severely increases performance of the model. Program name and university placement score also contribute to the system. Model is meant to be used as early as the second week of the spring semester.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "52012dd9-9545-44cc-8118-5048a08b3fc8",
        "parent": {
